            Margin Ratchet Name: {!relatedTo.Margin_Ratchet__r.Name}<br/>
            Margin Ratchet Type: {!relatedTo.Margin_Ratchet__r.Type__c}<br/>
            Event Type: {!relatedTo.Margin_Ratchet__r.Event_Type__c}<br/>
            Margin Ratchet Status: {!relatedTo.Margin_Ratchet__r.Status__c}<br/>
